 AND NODES USED IN THIS WORKFLOW  \n\n---\n\n## 🔍 Qwen-Image-Edit Diffusion Model\n### **Download the correct Qwen-Image-Edit 2509 model** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image-Edit_ComfyUI/tree/main/split_files/diffusion_models)\n\nSelect the appropriate size for your rig.\n\n📁 **Goes in in:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/qwen` \n\nIf you don't have a 'qwen' folder created, I recommend you create one.\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 Qwen-Image-Edit 8 Steps LoRA\n### **Download the correct Qwen-Image-Edit 2509 8 Steps LoRA** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/lightx2v/Qwen-Image-Lightning/tree/main)\n\nSelect the appropriate size for your rig.\n\n📁 **Goes in in:** `ComfyUI/models/loras/qwen` \n\nIf you don't have a 'qwen' folder created, I recommend you create one.\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 Qwen-Image-Edit Skin Detailer\n### **Download the correct Qwen-Image-Edit 2509 Skin Detailer** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/tlennon-ie/qwen-edit-skin/tree/main)\n\nSelect the appropriate size for your rig.  Experiment with different checkpoints.\n\n📁 **Goes in in:** `ComfyUI/models/loras/qwen` \n\nIf you don't have a 'qwen' folder created, I recommend you create one.\n\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 Load CLIP\n\n###  Download **qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors) or a bigger model from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/tree/main/split_files/text_encoders)\n\n📁 **Goes in:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders`  \n\n---\n\n## 🔍 Load VAE\n\n### Download **qwen_image_vae.safetensors** vae model from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors)  \n\n📁 **Goes in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`  \n\n---\n\n## 🛠 Nodes Installed from Manager  \n\n- SeedVR2 - Models will download at first use\n- There may be others based on your setup\n\n"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"}],"links"